summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Ninth Avenue Northwest from West 58th Street to West 65th Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 18658, creating Local Improvement District No. 1759 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
